  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libqmi</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libqmi</application> package contains a GLib-based library
      for talking to WWAN modems and devices which speak the Qualcomm MSM Interface
      (QMI) protocol.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

